HEADWORD: Ironstone
<hw>I"ron*stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <sn>1.</sn> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
hard, earthy ore of iron.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def><cref>ironstone china</cref>.</def>⟦br⟧
